{"tid":1434460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家睇睇！自由民主既重要性！一個活生生的例子","createTime":"2019-08-08T19:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T22:09:57.000Z","uid":113206,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"abf5ff8678038ba2e67ed42ee58f103c2369c360","tid":1434460,"uid":113206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9UdJ7mU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9UdJ7mU.png&h=1c70975c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係7到沒朋友<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4402797573487808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fdetail%2F4402797573487808&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=50871d09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4402797573487808</a>"},{"pid":"82cbe18c89a9c99f3c89023c1275d60dbda2319f","tid":1434460,"uid":113206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:19:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e94b559fc10c3c2ad94cbe1d72e8f059137b352","tid":1434460,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:20:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家覺得加返deadline升級好唔好？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n依家情況同上一個月差多<br />\n又係做好多嘢令到<span style=\"color: red;\">行動失去咗個目的</span>同埋冇時限搞到好似好迷失方向，和理非定勇武定包圍，行動上都係冇共識<br />\n加返deadline有好處<br />\n1.重申五大訴求，目標清晰，行動出師有名<br />\n2.訂立短中期行動計劃，例：今個禮拜和理非回合，唔回應就下個禮拜升級勇武行動<br />\n3.有計劃容易整合文宣<br />\n4.自己人有清晰目標，喺啲狗每日shift focus之下叫人專注返都易啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得 和理非&gt;deadline&gt;勇武升級 嘅抗爭概念<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431556</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"01251deaafb07336ad8f57826beff9196bdc6342","tid":1434460,"uid":113206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:23:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe3bdfe0b4bc537eef2822f724231c21300159da","tid":1434460,"uid":113206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ts637p7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTs637p7.png&h=aea25603&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mXVYwO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mXVYwO.png&h=24e500d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2q3ibRP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2q3ibRP.png&h=91479bec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbc34cc3567c2eef4f733b7e08e2da5df4557492","tid":1434460,"uid":275218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:29:23.000Z","msg":"文宣比深藍睇"},{"pid":"b180fbb1b86d3967aa0d557de4f917d47e122bef","tid":1434460,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:34:04.000Z","msg":"被黑警睇就岩架LA. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e79f9ba32caadddc1406b2327ae42c7f202999","tid":1434460,"uid":113206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:37:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"068bbc95bab6969a39bd715bf4ba51f63a98a093","tid":1434460,"uid":113206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:44:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0f4fffa5beb4396791800ad36e629af5ab21c0ef","tid":1434460,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:45:18.000Z","msg":"笑4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23882b1461f15cbc3e8d6409ceda9414a2653c45","tid":1434460,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:49:30.000Z","msg":"文宣材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608f157b57c6aa17c9f355b7c2ae23c18dfc74f9","tid":1434460,"uid":214192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:52:18.000Z","msg":"活生生嘅例子嚟<br />\n聽日，公安就會搵佢哋上門<br />\n聽日，佢哋全部都會被消失<br />\n共產黨唔會比國民贏，佢哋今次上訪一旦成功，將創下先例 以後就不斷有上訪出現<br />\n香港會唔會有朝一日變成咁樣？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會啊屌你老母支那共產黨，我地一定反抗到底，失去民主同自由比死更難受啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"f825804074e115e4186eaf741f0f2f55059716f7","tid":1434460,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:55:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好人好姐洗乜怕！光明正大！唔驚！黨同國家一定會幫你！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n打出嚟自己都笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49715a116204c520e6ced9927eaaf32d1f27b3d","tid":1434460,"uid":142735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:05:06.000Z","msg":"針唔拮到肉, 都唔知痛"},{"pid":"c94ca57151b9709b07ebc0d58e485fa0fc79a3b5","tid":1434460,"uid":113206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:11:27.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"0a6164f60719cfc40bf9adff0a42af7c063ce64c","tid":1434460,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f4197fe466092c0fc26b746b9b976fd72f7018","tid":1434460,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:16:42.000Z","msg":"好有用既文宣材料"},{"pid":"3109965afb4826d79019b117e29fac99c62dc317","tid":1434460,"uid":55529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和平上訪冇用既時候，可以做d咩呢"},{"pid":"556d3bf3b85447b3ced2262cca03b47e9049dc11","tid":1434460,"uid":113206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite